@0=~Brill sees you approaching and immediately reaches out his hand in expectation.~
@1=~"Your debt is nooooooaw 2000 copper pieces."~
@3=~"Here, take it."~
@4=~"I don't have it yet."~
@5=~"Listen. We both know that cup was worthless. I have serious business to attend to."~
@6=~Leave the counter.~
@8=~"Pike oooaf, demon. Go to the Oooarsman, where you're welcome.~
@14=~Behind the counter of the Rivergate tavern stands a tall, broad, toad-like humanoid. His skin is a wet, deep swamp green, covered with many colorful warts. He is busy wiping a bronze beer mug with a greasy rag. He doesn't seem to be paying you any attention. There is a dirty wooden plaque on the bar.~
@15=~"I urge you not to interact with this one... The slaadi do not *know* themselves and only bring destruction to the multiverse."~
@17=~"Hey, can I get some service?"~
@18=~Inspect the wooden plaque on the counter.~
@19=~Truth: "Hey, you're a slaad, aren't you?"~
@20=~Joke: "Hey, you're a hezrou, aren't you?"~
@21=~Joke: "Hey, you're a hydroloth, aren't you?"~
@22=~"Hey, you're a slaad, aren't you?"~
@23=~"Hey, you're a hezrou, aren't you?"~
@24=~"Hey, you're a hydroloth, aren't you?"~
@25=~You feel the essence of chaos emanating from the creature. You know it is a slaad. "Brother in chaos, nice to meet you."~
@27=~Behind the counter of the Rivergate tavern, just as before, stands a tall, broad, toad-like humanoid. His skin is a wet, deep swamp green, covered with many colorful warts. He is busy wiping another beer mug. He doesn't seem to be paying you any attention. There is a dirty wooden plaque on the bar.~
@28=~"I urge you not to interact with this one... The slaadi do not *know* themselves and only bring destruction to the multiverse."~
@30=~"Hey, can I get some service?"~
@31=~Inspect the wooden plaque on the counter.~
