@35=~"Hey, you're a slaad, aren't you?"~
@36=~"Hey, you're a hezrou, aren't you?"~
@37=~"Hey, you're a hydroloth, aren't you?"~
@38=~You feel the essence of chaos emanating from the creature. You know it is a slaad. "Brother in chaos, nice to meet you."~
@40=~Brill the slaad looks at you with his wide eyes. "Whooat d'ya want?"~
@42=~"Hey. I changed my mind. I want to help you with your stolen possession."~
@43=~"I have your possession. I didn't think it would be a vial of karach..."~
@44=~"I cannot return your karach. It is gone."~
@45=~"You won't believe it, Brill." You lower your voice to a whisper. "Black Joseph took your karach."~
@46=~"You won't believe it, Brill." You lower your voice to a whisper. "Black Joseph took your karach."~
@47=~"I have decided not to retrieve your possession. Any other ideas on how I can get you to help me?"~
@48=~"I am still working to find your possession."~
@49=~Inspect the wooden plaque on the counter.~
@50=~"I tried to go over there to talk to Joseph, but... I ended up in the Ditch. How come?"~
@51=~"I tried to go over there to talk to Joseph, but... I ended up in the Ditch. How come?"~
@52=~"I have some questions."~
@54=~"I would like to rest on your couch." ~
@55=~Leave the counter.~
@57=~He doesn't answer. Instead, he bumps his elbow against a wooden plaque on the counter.~
@59=~Inspect the wooden plaque on the counter.~
@60=~Truth: "Hey, you're a slaad, aren't you?"~
